videos.description: Matt Linehan's deep pass into traffic is tipped and intercepted by Dre Terrell, who makes the catch on his back.
videos.headline: Sacramento State's Terrell makes acrobatic interception in end zone

videos.description: Elijah Dotson finds a crease in the line, and scampers past the Idaho defense for a big run.
videos.headline: Dotson explodes through big hole for 25-yard gain

videos.description: Matt Linehan avoids the pass rush and connects with Aaron Duckworth, who tiptoes along the sidelines for a big gain.
videos.headline: Linehan eludes rush, finds Duckworth for huge 49-yard pickup

videos.description: Matt Linehan scrambles to his left and throws back across his body to find Jacob Sannon in the end zone.
videos.headline: Linehan connects with wide-open Sannon for 8-yard TD

videos.description: Reuben Mwehla outruns the defense and hauls in the deep touchdown pass.
videos.headline: Mwehla burns his man, catches 35-yard TD

videos.description: George Obinna forces the fumble which Seperini Aumua recovers after a mad dash for the ball.
videos.headline: Obinna sacks QB, Sacramento State wins scramble for fumble

videos.description: Aaron Duckworth's big day continues, as he rips off another big run.
videos.headline: Duckworth bursts out of the backfield for 28-yard gain

videos.description: Aaron Duckworth easily runs through the Sacramento State defense for his first touchdown of the season.
videos.headline: Duckworth finds end zone on 18-yard run
